c: 30
v: 9
t: "Ese (abahakanyi) ntibatambagira isi ngo barebe uko iherezo ry’abababanjirije ryagenze? Bari abanyembaraga kubarusha, banahinga isi kubarusha bakanayibyaza umusaruro, ndetse bakanayubaka kurusha uko bo bayubaka. Banagezweho n’Intumwa zabo zibazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara (ariko barazihinyura, maze Allah arabarimbura). Allah ntiyigeze abarenganya, ahubwo ni bo ubwabo bihemukiye"